    "Table 2 shows the quantitative analysis of the six evaluation criteria which assess the various aspects of the interaction between the tutor bot and students.",
    "• Tutor bot enacted the script",
    "The tutor bot followed the prompt script in 45 out of 51 instances, demonstrating a high level of adherence to the prescribed guidelines.",
    "However, despite this significant adherence, there were occasions when the tutor bot deviated from the script or overlooked certain instructions meant for the learners.",
    "Similarly, some students responded with questions or requests for assistance rather than directly answering the questions as instructed."
  ]
